w-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t<h4>Thanks, great support!</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tBy <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mosaicbc\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e5296ff77acb064f9d708927036dcd76?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mosaicbc\">mosaicbc</a>,\n\t\t\t<span class=\"review-date\">April 29, 2016</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.5.1</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\n\t\t<p>We really appreciate receiving a non-profit rate for this wonderful plugin. We work with immigrants and refugees in Canada and this calendar will greatly help us in our mission. Thank you!\n</p>\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t<h4>Only few hours from install to implementation !!!</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tBy <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/tveden\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02d48467b6d87e30d662c3e36c803520?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/tveden\">Tveden</a>,\n\t\t